### Question Design Criteria

| Criterion | ✅ Good | ❌ Bad |
|-----------|---------|--------|
| **Clarity** | "Allocate $500K across paid search, content, events" | "Explain SEO best practices" |
| **Signal** | "CAC +40%, CVR -15%. Diagnose root cause" | "List the AIDA stages" |
| **Depth** | "Choose awareness vs demand gen vs retention. Justify with budget constraints" | "Should we use social media?" |
| **Realism** | "CEO wants B2B entry. How reposition B2C brand?" | "Design a Facebook ad" |
| **Discrimination** | "When does multi-touch attribution mislead? Give scenarios" | "What is multi-touch attribution?" |
| **Role alignment** | Senior: execution \| Director: strategy \| VP: vision/revenue | |

