### Reference Sections

#### Glossary (≥10 entries)
**G1. STP**: Segmentation→Targeting→Positioning. Use: market entry, launches, strategy
**G2. 4Ps/7Ps**: Product/Price/Place/Promotion (+People/Process/Physical). Use: campaign planning, GTM
**G3. AIDA**: Attention→Interest→Desire→Action. Use: copywriting, campaigns, funnels
**G4. CAC**: (Sales+Marketing)/New Customers. Related: LTV, payback period
**G5. LTV**: ARPU×Lifespan or (ARPU×Margin)/Churn. Healthy: LTV:CAC ≥3:1
**G6. Attribution**: Last-Click, First-Click, Linear, Time-Decay, Position-Based, Data-Driven
**G7. Brand Equity**: Value premium. Measured: awareness, associations, quality, loyalty
**G8. Market Segmentation**: Demographics, psychographics, behavior, geography, firmographics
**G9. Content Marketing**: Blogs, videos, podcasts, whitepapers, webinars for inbound/SEO
**G10. MQL**: Marketing Qualified Lead. Use: scoring, funnel, sales alignment

